HIGH PERFORMING WOOLWORTHS + DAN MURPHY’S + 9 SHOPS
VIC, Hoppers Crossing, Cnr Hogans & Derrimut Roads


• Historically high performing neighbourhood shopping centre anchored by a Woolworths Supermarket (in % rent) and new Dan Murphy’s (Lease expiry 2025)

• Rare net lease to Woolworths with a consistent track record of turnover and rental growth

• Impeccably maintained centre (5,568sqm GLA*) including only nine (9) specialty stores

• Highly exposed 2.212 ha* corner infill site, being the premium convenience centre position within the fastest growing municipality in Victoria

• Access and frontages to two (2) major western Melbourne thoroughfares

• Convenient at grade car park for 251 vehicles* (4.50 cars/100sqm*)

• Main Trade Area of 35,690 people, expected to grow by 17% to 41,870 by 2026**

• 100% leased providing Net Income of $1,930,000 per annum*

The property is being offered by way of a Private Sale.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Hogans Corner Shopping Centre - Double Woolworths Anchor

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE Victorian Retail Investments, in conjunction with Stonebridge Property Group, are delighted to present for your consideration an exceptional freestanding, single tenanted, Victorian retail investment property located in metropolitan Melbourne.

Bunnings Hoppers Crossing offers the following key attributes:

* Long term lease to Wesfarmers Limited subsidiary, Bunnings Group Limited
* Strong trading store with unrivalled position in the heart of Victoria's largest bulky goods precinct (Source: Deep End Services)
* Situated in a major population growth area of Melbourne (25km* from Melbourne CBD)
* Favourable net lease structure with annual CPI increases
* Substantial site of 26,880sqm*, with extensive exposure to Old Geelong Road (167* metre frontage)
* Net income of $1,230,000pa* (from 22 March 2012)

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: BUNNINGS HOPPERS CROSSING - DOMINANT VICTORIAN RETAIL INVESTMENT

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE Large Format Retail is pleased to present this high profile showroom in the heart of the dominant retail strip, Old Geelong Road

2/194 Old Geelong Road, Hoppers Crossing enjoys a prominent position fronting the bustling carriageway within a small centre comprising other prominent retailers.

The exciting opportunity includes;

*1,412sqm for lease
*Double Auto Doors to the front, suspended ceiling, air conditioning, 10 pair phone lines, rear roller door, warehouse dividing wall, amenities and a kitchenette.
*Bold showroom and pylon signage.
*Ample customer car parking and ease of access.
*Central position on Old Geelong Road.
*20metres of frontage to Old Geelong Road.
*Unparalleled residential growth in the local catchment
*176,000 people within a 20 minute drive time with a median annual household income above the Melbourne average


Call now to secure a time to inspect or request a detailed leasing prospectus.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Unit 2 / 194 Old Geelong Road Hoppers Crossing

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE Large Format Retail are pleased to present for lease Shop 4 at the Shoppers Crossing Centre, 283 Old Geelong Road, Hoppers Crossing.

This 1,200sqm showroom is strategically positioned central to the Old Geelong Road strip amongst national brands JB Hi-Fi. Petbarn, Beacon Lighting, Rays Outdoors, Snooze, Forty Winks plus many more. Shoppers Crossing is identified amongst the retailers on the strip as being the heart and most dominant retail position on Old Geelong Road.

The showroom features a prominent two storey faA§ade with bold showroom signage, plasterboard ceiling, air conditioning, warehouse with rear loading and ample on-grade car parking.

Key Aspects of the opportunity include;
- Rare opportunity in Hoppers Crossing's hottest location

- Join national neighbours JB Hi-Fi, Snooze, Super Cheap Auto, Petbarn + more

- Modern showroom fit out available as is

- Multi-directional access via traffic lights from Old Geelong Road
